Convenience function for  load    function definition:  inline QDataStream  operator (QDataStream  stream, const Transform  f)    parameters:     Parameter  Type  Description      stream  QDataStream    Stream to load the transform from    f  const  Transform    Transform to store loaded information       output:  ( QDataStream   ) Returns the stream without the transform data   example: Transform *in = Transform::make("Example(property1=value1,property2=value2)");

